# TUI demo — interactive dashboard
Output tui.webm
Output tui.gif

Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set FontSize 15
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Type "daedalus tui"
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Navigate project list
Down
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 1s
Up
Sleep 1s

# Start a project
Type "s"
Sleep 4s

# Attach to session
Type "a"
Sleep 3s

# Detach and quit
Type "q"
Sleep 2s
